{"tid":167764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[勇士再現]指林鄭曾駐英近兩年不合參選資格 覆核王申司法覆核","createTime":"2017-03-23T05:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T18:58:14.000Z","uid":77196,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a40d83ffa02f79930d3aa340efb8b2301f0802ae","tid":167764,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T05:23:43.000Z","msg":"特首參選人林鄭月娥在2004年9月至2006年3月間出任香港駐倫敦經濟貿易辦事處處長並居於英國。「長洲覆核王」郭卓堅質疑林鄭月娥違反《行政長官選舉條例》，入稟申請司法覆核，指選舉事務處的總選舉主任批准林鄭月娥參選的決定有問題，要求法庭頒令取消她的參選資格。<br />\n<br />\n郭卓堅指，根據《行政長官選舉條例》，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>參選人在行政長官職位出缺之日前在香港通常居住連續不少於20年，即至少由1997年6月30日起便在香港通常居住。郭指林鄭在2004年至2006年間，以英國居民身分居於英國</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n案件答辯人是總選舉主任黃思文。郭在入稟後見記者，他指黃思文有疏忽，「咁都畀佢選」，他又指入稟的目的是要讓林鄭「選倒都十五十六」，令她擔心自己有沒有資格做特首。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n推到條死八婆仆街冚家產 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187e17ae73a7e704150fc05c320d9f40f3703f23","tid":167764,"uid":36543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T05:29:53.000Z","msg":"係咪有上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"364f94c46df1ee50e4dcd221a70461f78d8be6db","tid":167764,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T05:30:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2fcef29cf4f1693a9d054b380255adb76afd4cf9","tid":167764,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T05:31:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪有上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能有人報料俾佢聽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e36ee5e7b4e3b86ee45bc1565b86bfe1d6ecdab0","tid":167764,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci